==English==

===Adjective===
'''ginge'''
# (''pejorative'') shortened form of [[ginger]]

===Verb===
'''ginge'''
# Action of posting an already posted link/article/joke etc, to the newsgroup uk.rec.motorcycles [[http://groups.google.com/group/uk.rec.motorcycles?hl=en UKRM]].  Also the chorus of ridicule offered by readers of the link/article/post repeated. Derivation: named in honour of the sobriquet of a rufous regular of the newsgroup, who was notoriously prone to such solecisms, but he's better now. 

A valid, yet invariably unsuccessful, defence against accusations of "Gingeing" may be to have Googled for said link/article/joke and not found a prior reference.
----

